# 📚 APSCHE Practice Portal

A 100% original full-stack clone of APSCHE Web Options Entry Portal. 
Built for practice and learning purposes using MERN stack. 
Fully responsive and deployed on both GitHub Pages + Vercel.

## 🌐 Live Demo

- **Frontend - GitHub Pages**: [Click Here](https://jarajapugowtham.github.io/Apsche.practicemodel/)
- **Frontend - Vercel**: [Click Here](https://apsche-practicemodel.vercel.app)
- **Backend API - Render**: `https://apsche-practicemodel.onrender.com`

## 🛠 Tech Stack

**Frontend:**
- HTML5
- CSS3 
- JavaScript
- Deployed on: GitHub Pages, Vercel

**Backend:**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- CORS enabled for multiple origins
- Deployed on: Render

**Database:**
- MongoDB + Mongoose [Ready to Connect]

**Tools Used:**
- Git & GitHub
- VS Code
- Postman for API testing
- bcryptjs for password hashing

## ✨ Features

- **Pixel-perfect UI clone** of APSCHE portal
- **Fully responsive** - works on mobile, tablet, desktop
- **Full MERN Architecture** - Frontend + Backend + Database ready
- **User Authentication** - Register & Login API endpoints
- **Colleges API** - Fetch college data from backend
- **CORS Configured** - Works with Vercel and GitHub Pages
- **Form validation** and smooth interactions
- **Practice web options entry flow**

